title: It's Going To Happen Quickly
itunes:title: It's Going To Happen Quickly
description:
There are some moments God has prepared to do a quick work in your life. The obstacle you’re facing may look permanent, but in a moment, God can turn it around. Stay encouraged. You’re about to step into a sudden breakthrough!To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
